    <div class="section-label">Education Policy</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">NEP 2020</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">National Education Policy 2020 — India's landmark education reform explained in English and Hindi.</p>
    <div class="nep-lang-tabs">
      <div class="nep-lang-tab active" onclick="switchNep('en',this)">🇬🇧 English</div>
      <div class="nep-lang-tab" onclick="switchNep('hi',this)">🇮🇳 हिंदी</div>
